**Section 80C** allows deductions up to ₹1,50,000 per year from your taxable income under the old tax regime. Eligible investments include ELSS, PPF, LIC premium, EPF contribution, NSC, 5-year FD, ULIP, and home loan principal repayment, plus tuition fees for up to 2 children.
